Repository Name Unauthorized: Air Force Enlisted Heritage Research Institute
Notes: Preservation of and records pretaining to U.S. Air Force and U.S. Army Aeronautical Division, Air Service, Air Corps, and Air Forces in the development of air power to defend the United States. The collection contains artifacts, art collections, pictorial exhibits, written and oral documentation, audiovisuals, equipment, and selected aircraft parts.
Source of Repository Data: Alabama Department of Archives and History
